column5: Great pictures and ya gotta love the wildlife, but what the heck is the bear chewing on ??
Lew that cat pic is what i wanted to post in your thread sometime back  The bear is eating a donut the kids left outside
I kind of thought that was a donut but figured "no way" hahaha  The pic of the cat and deer is priceless too, infact I enjoy any pics of wild animals.
Love the pics,watch out for the kids as I know you do.Not sure the dog could take that on?,maybe ? lol.

Thats a big bear man. No way the dogs can take that on lol.  Most around here are smaller black bears.  Lew, the pic of the deer and our old cat is priceless, shes gone now. They played for a good half hour, touching noses numerous times. It was awesome to watch from the window. We didnt want to disturb them.  The top pic is of a few tornados trying to form over the pow wow grounds in RRFN a few years back. Boy was the mrs scared lol.
